694baba8-b80c-4ee5-ac90-d9efb4491cb0.text: Hello there, what's going on here?

dc2ec5ee-6e0b-4bac-bdba-21aa708e26f7.text:

cleverer to be running so da sickies from da zogres
don't dead ya.

9f239431-bcb3-480f-a013-e01e7ee6cee6.text:

c8757497-ede8-47b6-ac11-646783a3343c.title: Grish
c8757497-ede8-47b6-ac11-646783a3343c.text:
Da sickies is when yous creature goes like orange till
green and then goes 'Urggghhhh!' 
~ Grish imitates falling down with only the white of his
eyes visible. ~

options.text: Can I help in any way?

dbc230b4-483b-419f-8ed2-9103cb52cdde.title: Grish

like was before.

562b0c4a-356d-46fe-bde9-64805e4a9fa5.text:

Sorry, yous creatures, but yous is too green behind da
